{"tid":887000,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【金庸逝世】習近平表示哀悼","createTime":"2018-11-02T14:10:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T14:18:26.000Z","uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9f67e077b03c9ffe4ee2b8d85a543adc7df0d024","tid":887000,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T14:10:12.000Z","msg":"香港著名武俠小說作家金庸（查良鏞）上月30日離世，終年94歲。中共中央總書記、國家主席習近平對查良鏞的逝世表示哀悼，並對其親屬表示慰問。中聯辦主任王志民今晚更專程到查良鏞家中，向查夫人林樂怡轉達習近平等中央領導，對查良鏞逝世的哀悼和對親屬予以慰問。林樂怡對習等中央領導的關心問候，表示感謝。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，查良鏞逝世後，現任及前任國家領導人與中共高層，包括李克強、韓正、孫春蘭、黃坤明、朱鎔基、溫家寶、張德江、李嵐清、劉延東、李源潮、王漢斌、廖暉等人，都以不同方式表示哀悼，並向其親屬表示慰問。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181102/588\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181102%2F588&d=VfD9y1t7vWCjeKqaFPmh%2BEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=b6cfd7e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181102%2F588&h=0c5839b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181102/588</a>"},{"pid":"4a412680ee27567692a0a9f82053af1ef2dc751a","tid":887000,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T14:10:57.000Z","msg":"佢識字架咩"},{"pid":"27f256de2604e413866d406745d22fbfc01a8a0a","tid":887000,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T14:18:26.000Z","msg":"查生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}